description:
Listen to my podcast on Nebula now: https://go.nebula.tv/captainmidnight
The Office has so many great episodes, but there's lowlights as well. IMDB seems to think the worst is season 8's "Get the Girl. In this video, I get into the episode. Andy, Erin, Nellie and why it just doesn't work for people.
